# CHANGELOG

History is a mirror.

## Version 0.0.12.25 (Merry X'mas!)

* Re-organize blueprints,  models and Templates.
* Remove Flask-admin, implement a simple admin interface.
* Clean codes according to pep8.

## Version 0.1

* First public preview release.

## Version 0.1.1

Support Flask v0.10.1, HTML5 Boilerplate v4.3.0, Twitter Bootstrap v3.3.1, jQuery v1.11.1.

## Version 0.2

* Upgrade to [Flask v0.11](https://www.palletsprojects.com/blog/flask-011-released/).
* Upgrade to Bootstrap3.3.6, jQuery 2.2.4, etc.
* Rewrite unittests.
* Use [Cloudfare CDN](https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com).
* Use [Flask-Restful](http://flask-restful-cn.readthedocs.io) to build APIs.
* Deprecate setup.py, use requirments.txt instead.
* Deprecate Flask-Script, use Flask cli instead.
* Deprecate Flask-Babel.
